id.description: User-specified id. Ths is used in an output group or an output.

mediaPackageSettings.description: Destination settings for a MediaPackage output; one destination for both encoders. See Media Package Settings for more details.

multiplexSettings.description: Destination settings for a Multiplex output; one destination for both encoders. See Multiplex Settings for more details.

settings.description: Destination settings for a standard output; one destination for each redundant encoder. See Settings for more details.
